{"word":"Miracles","slug":"miracles","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Miracles</b> Catalogue of, prior to Christ's ministry:<br/> - Creation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1'>Gen 1</a> <br/> - Flood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=7'>Gen 7</a> <br/> - Confusion of tongues<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=9'>Gen 11:9</a> <br/> - Fire on Abraham's sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=17'>Gen 15:17</a> <br/> - Conception of Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=17'>Gen 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=12'>Gen 18:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=2'>Gen 21:2</a> <br/> - Destruction of Sodom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19'>Gen 19</a> <br/> - Lot's wife turned to salt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=26'>Gen 19:26</a> <br/> - Closing of the wombs of Abimelech's household<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=18'>Gen 20:18</a> <br/> - Opening of Hagar's eyes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=19'>Gen 21:19</a> <br/> - Conception of Jacob and Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=21'>Gen 25:21</a> <br/> - Opening of Rachel's womb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=22'>Gen 30:22</a> <br/> - Flaming bush<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=2'>Exo 3:2</a> <br/> - Transformation of Moses' rod into a serpent<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=4'>Exo 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=30'>Exo 4:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=10'>Ex