/a><br/> b Cures Naaman of leprosy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=19'>2Ki 5:19</a><br/> b Smites Gehazi with leprosy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=27'>2Ki 5:27</a><br/> b Causes the ax to float<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=6'>2Ki 6:6</a><br/> b Reveals the counsel of the king of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=12'>2Ki 6:12</a><br/> b Causes the eyes of his servant to be opened<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=17'>2Ki 6:17</a><br/> b Smites with blindness the army of the king of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=18'>2Ki 6:18</a><br/> b the dead man restored to life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=21'>2Ki 13:21</a><br/> - Destruction of Sennacherib's army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=35'>2Ki 19:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=37&verse=36'>Isa 37:36</a> <br/> - Return of the shadow on the sun dial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=11'>2Ki 20:11</a> <br/> - Hezekiah's cure<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=21'>Isa 38:21</a> <br/> - Deliverance of Shadrach, Meshach and Abed-Nego<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=27'>Dan 3:27</a> <br/> - Deliverance of Daniel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=22'>Dan 6:22</a> <br/> - The sea calmed, on Jonah being cast into it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=15'>Jon 1:15</a> <br/> - Jonah in the fish's belly<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=17'>Jon 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=2&verse=10'>Jon 2:10</a> <br/> - Jonah's gourd<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=4&verse=7'>Jon 4:7</a> <br/> - Conception by Elizabeth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=18'>Luk 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=25'>Luk 1:25</a> <br/> - The incarnation of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=25'>Mat 1:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=80'>Luk 1:80</a> <br/> - The appearance of the star of Bethlehem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=9'>Mat 2:9</a> <br/> - The deliverance of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=23'>Mat 2:23</a> <br/> Miracles of Jesus, in chronological order:<br/> - Water made into wine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=11'>Joh 2:11</a> <br/> - Heals the nobleman's son<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=54'>Joh 4:54</a> <br/> - Draught of fishes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=11'>Luk 5:11</a> <br/> - Heals the demoniac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=26'>Mar 1:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=36'>Luk 4:36</a> <br/> - Heals Peter's mother-in-law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=17'>Mat 8:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=31'>Mar 1:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=39'>Luk 4:39</a> <br/> - Cleanses the leper<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=4'>Mat 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=45'>Mar 1:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=16'>Luk 5:16</a> <br/> - Heals the paralytic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles